{{Top|leg}}
'''Tomuons''' were long-horned, woolly herd animals that were native to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Askaji/Legends|Askaj]]. Their coats were turned into a highly prized fabric. [[Askajian/Legends|Askajians]] also used their meat, [[Milk/Legends|milk]], hooves, fat, and bones for food and other essential items. It was rumored that [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine's]] robes were made of tomuon wool.

{{Creature-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
Tomuons are sometimes conflictingly spelled "Toumon".

